dataIdInfo.idAbs:
The dataset represents the departments of Tchad.

This is an operational dataset for humanitarian response. The boundaries are not yet recognized officially by the government but knowledgeable, local technical stakeholder participated to the development of these layers.

Consts.useLimit: See the COD/FOD Registry Terms of Use. This does not replace any terms of use information provided with the dataset.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from an email from the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. The layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Admin 1 name spelling "Hadjer Lamis" changed to "Hadjer-Lamis" for consistency with Administrative Level 1.
